item.title: [HBASE-16084] Clean up the stale references in javadoc
item.description:
From TestHFileOutputFormat2 , e.g.:

 * Simple test for {@link CellSortReducer} and {@link HFileOutputFormat2}.

CellSortReducer doesn't exist.

From TestSerialization.java :

   * Create a table of name <code>name</code> with {@link COLUMNS} for

COLUMNS cannot be found.

This issue is to clean up the stale references in javadoc.
item.summary: Clean up the stale references in javadoc

status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.
